affixes.name: Fortified
affixes.description: Non-boss enemies have 20% more health and inflict up to 30% increased damage.

affixes.name: Inspiring
affixes.description: Some non-boss enemies have an inspiring presence that strengthens their allies.

affixes.name: Grievous
affixes.description: Injured players suffer increasing damage over time until healed.

affixes.name: Shrouded
affixes.description: Nathrezim infiltrators have disguised themselves among enemies throughout the dungeon. Cartel Ta will reward you handsomely for assisting in their capture.
